PrecisAuthority to enter into an individual AGREEMENT RESPECTING BIOLOGY CASEWORK ANALYSIS with the Province of MANITOBA, the Territory of NUNAVUT and the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES which provides for the sharing of costs associated with the forensic analysis of biological evidence arising out of criminal investigations of designated offences.
